A Magician from 1-60 gives up all forms of defense for a supposedly superior pet and the ability to nuke, along with that we can debuff and damage shield.  I guess CoH, which doesn't work in most of the luclin high level zones, is enough to impose on mages the inability to be 'defined' in any aspect of this game.<br>
