<br>
If these go live and their availability is not so limited as to be nearly non-existant I don't see any reason to continue playing at this point.  At least not as a mage.  I can't see knowingly burdening a raid or a group with my inferior abilities, even if they don't mind - it's not fair of me.  FFS Druids can cast clarity in the form of a skin buff, regen you.. I'm sorry - it's beyond me.<br>
